{"type":"message","id":"a8a898eb","parentId":"80c7d05c","timestamp":"2026-06-13T16:00:58.634Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"4ed4f542477048dea2dbdf4d1f20bac5","toolName":"composio__COMPOSIO_MULTI_EXECUTE_TOOL","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"data\":{\"results\":[{\"response\":{\"successful\":true,\"data\":{\"has_results\":true,\"news_results\":[{\"date\":\"3 weeks ago\",\"link\":\"https://www.csoonline.com/article/4176701/as-ai-speeds-coding-cve-lite-cli-keeps-security-deliberately-ai-free.html\",\"published_at\":\"2026-05-25 07:00:00 UTC\",\"snippet\":\"The OWASP-backed tool scans JavaScript and TypeScript lockfiles locally, aiming to help developers catch and remediate dependency risks...\",\"source\":\"CSO Online\",\"title\":\"As AI speeds coding, CVE Lite CLI keeps security deliberately AI-free\"},{\"date\":\"Dec 17, 2025\",\"link\":\"https://developers.googleblog.com/introducing-agent-development-kit-for-typescript-build-ai-agents-with-the-power-of-a-code-first-approach/\",\"published_at\":\"2025-12-17 08:00:00 UTC\",\"snippet\":\"Build powerful, autonomous multi-agent AI systems with Agent Development Kit (ADK) for TypeScript. A code-first, open-source framework.\",\"source\":\"blog.google\",\"title\":\"Introducing Agent Development Kit for TypeScript: Build AI Agents with the Power of a Code-First Approach\"},{\"date\":\"Jan 28, 2026\",\"link\":\"https://www.devclass.com/ai-ml/2026/01/28/typescript-inventor-anders-hejlsberg-ai-is-a-big-regurgitator-of-stuff-someone-has-done/4079582\",\"published_at\":\"2026-01-28 08:00:00 UTC\",\"snippet\":\"Microsoft technical fellow Anders Hejlsberg, inventor of both C# and TypeScript, said that existing languages are the ones […]\",\"source\":\"DevClass\",\"title\":\"TypeScript inventor Anders Hejlsberg: AI is 'a big regurgitator of stuff someone has done'\"},{\"date\":\"Mar 5, 2026\",\"link\":\"https://www.infoq.com/news/2026/03/ai-reshapes-language-choice/\",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-05 08:00:00 UTC\